- Asm-Pro v1.15/v1.16 (c) Solo/Genetic
Nice work Solo, but please fix the bugs I've told you about a long time ago!


- DBug v1.1 (c) Dietmar Heidrich
Old Debugger (from 1992) that came with the OMA package. Although I don't like
